Quickstrike was knocked off his feet by the blasts and slung 
backwards a few feet.  He tried to recollect while himself 
staggering to his feet. 

Waspinator flew to the right to avoid the ships attacks.  He raised 
his gun and fired an explosive stinger at the spacecraft.

Inferno covered his eyes with his free hand as the explosions blew 
derbies his way.  He continued taking aim waiting to see if any of 
the ships crew would try to leave the ship to fight.
